      <td width="16">&nbsp;</td>
      <td width="620"> <a href="typed/3e.htm#3g">Photos of a Type D desk in Studio 
        3G of Broadcasting House <span class="red">added May 2023</span>.</a><br />
        <a href="tapes/btr2.htm#ap">A note about the use of BTR/2s 
        at Alexandra Palace in the 1960s <span class="red">added January 2023.</span></a><br />
	  <a href="parl/mb.htm">A description of facilities at Millbank, 
        home of the BBC's coverage of Parliament <span class="red">added May 2021</span>.</a><br /> 
        <a href="new.htm">Click here for details of other recent additions.</a> </td>
